Improved Grab	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:AstralDreadnaughtRaceTrait.SpecialAttack.Extraordinary	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:To use this ability, the astral dreadnought must hit with its bite attack. If it gets a hold, it automatically deals bite damage and can try to swallow the opponent. An astral dreadnought that hits with a claw attack grabs as above. If it gets a hold, it picks up the opponent and transfers it to the mouth as a partial action, automatically dealing bite damage as above.	KEY:Astral Dreadnaught ~ Improved Grab																											SOURCEPAGE:MotP
