Plane Shift	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:UmbralBanyanRaceTrait.SpecialQuality.Supernatural	VISIBLE:YES	DESC:As a free action, an umbral banyan can shift itself and any grappled opponents to a forest on the Plane of Shadow for 5 rounds, as the Plane Shift spell. The umbral banyan and any creatures within 20 feet of it return to the original spot on the Material Plane at the end of that time, unless the banyan is destroyed in the meantime, in which case any surviving opponents must find their own way home. Umbral banyans native to the Plane of Shadow can plane shift to a forest on the Material Plane in the same way.	KEY:Umbral Banyan ~ Plane Shift																											SOURCEPAGE:MotP
